title: Fox Corporation
added: In September 2021, Fox Corporation buys [[TMZ]] from  [[WarnerMedia]] in a deal worth about $50 million. TMZ will operate under the [[Fox Entertainment]] branch of Fox Corporation. <ref>{{Cite web|title=Fox Entertainment Closes Acquisition Of TMZ From WarnerMedia|url=https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/fox-entertainment-closes-acquisition-tmz-201509654.html|access-date=2021-09-13|website=www.yahoo.com|language=en-US}}</ref>
